{"tid":1048902,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[JobsDB]就欠一個 PHP 人","createTime":"2019-03-06T02:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T02:23:48.000Z","uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6cd4767777985f81b78311a4fa506d97748e55ee","tid":1048902,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:06:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，上個 post 反應熱烈，決定再開多個 post ;)<br />\n<br />\nTL;DR:<br />\n<br />\n今次會考慮啲有少少經驗（1 - 3 年）嘅 developer<br />\n免費零食野飲<br />\n年尾視乎表現發花紅，出色嘅兩三個月花紅都有<br />\n<br />\n介紹返，我本身係寫 code 嘅，兩年前開左呢間公司，有幾個長期合作嘅 project 跟緊，最近都有唔少人想 outsource 啲 project 過來，所以想請個人幫下手<br />\n<br />\n技術方面主要係做 Web，我地用開 PHP，另外有時都需要用 react natvie 去寫 app<br />\n<br />\n呢份工有挑戰嘅位係學識點樣做個 scale up 到嘅網站，因為手頭上啲網站本身都幾多人上，要學識點 tune 下啲 server，或者改 code 去 support 到好多人同時在線而又唔會死機之類<br />\n<br />\n有三類野係我地長期做緊嘅：<br />\n<br />\nShopping cart，我地有個台灣伙伴用緊我地寫嘅一套 shopping cart 系統，而家都仲有 actively develop 緊新 feature，有時仲會開 FB 直播，啲流量會一下子衝哂入來，嗰段時間可能就要睇實個網<br />\nWordpress，有唔少 request 係要做啲速食網站，我地都係用 wordpress 去做，基本上有哂標準程序，跟住我地套寫法去做就得<br />\n另外就係出面接返來嘅 project，真係乜花款都有，寫過 Wordpress, Drupal, React Native, ...，好多野可以學到<br />\n目前需要你識嘅係：<br />\n<br />\nPHP<br />\nSQL (MySQL)<br />\nHTML, CSS, JS<br />\n識呢啲有分加：<br />\n<br />\nLaravel<br />\nWordpress <br />\nMagento<br />\nnode.js<br />\nReact Native<br />\n人工方面就睇你經驗同識幾多野再定，1 - 3 年經驗都會考慮<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.jobsdb.com/hk/en/job/%E5%B0%B1%E6%AC%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B-php-%E4%BA%BA-100003006876576\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.jobsdb.com%2Fhk%2Fen%2Fjob%2F%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B-php-%25E4%25BA%25BA-100003006876576&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXh3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=82dee080\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.jobsdb.com/hk/en/job/%E5%B0%B1%E6%AC%A0%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B-php-%E4%BA%BA-100003006876576</a>"},{"pid":"65814eee86cdc0d87faae46d9556f377da18f58e","tid":1048902,"uid":229095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:09:10.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"52e6e7da8c436bb7e675215b6b81f80bd3a1186d","tid":1048902,"uid":70159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"Php 不了"},{"pid":"bc60bee0a372da0837453a752647a4da2c7e0634","tid":1048902,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:39:11.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"bbd7ed2defb88c5f82d640a843aa5a9d9d317df9","tid":1048902,"uid":56323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:45:48.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"3b66b1c96236a5b9e208c699a1a16725262c30d5","tid":1048902,"uid":34223,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"要上嚟連登搵傻仔做你份工 真係好撚悲哀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07beb9e48ecb2b0e8411bbef7cfc8b7fe3d13fd","tid":1048902,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52e6e7da8c436bb7e675215b6b81f80bd3a1186d","tid":1048902,"uid":70159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T02:10:15.000Z","msg":"Php 不了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:00:19.000Z","msg":"Same reply I had in mind😂😂😂"},{"pid":"dfd6c6b24dcad9c37d5f552c963b38a3da3c8179","tid":1048902,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:00:49.000Z","msg":"$9k salary 不了"},{"pid":"cb56e1929054a3e24d30305063e6b174be279253","tid":1048902,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:08:27.000Z","msg":"一年經驗又要識capacity management一般都係啲好勁嘅人，都係得17k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e316aff052ffc2c97364fd92f2cb56a312b41f9","tid":1048902,"uid":61398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b1574dd0c472fef9cc019f82070ff83fbb623b36","tid":1048902,"uid":169656,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"每次見到呢d寫web既細公司<br />\n<br />\n我就諗起 n 年前屌尻員工接freelan